  <section id="artifact1" class="page" role="region" aria-label="Artifact 1: AI Lab Chatbot Development">
    <h2>Artifact 1: AI Lab - No-Code Chatbot Assistant Development</h2>

    <p><strong>Introduction:</strong> This artifact demonstrates my hands-on experience developing a no-code AI chatbot assistant using leading platforms, showcasing technical and strategic skills in AI deployment.</p>

    <h3>Project Overview</h3>
    <p>The AI Lab Chatbot Assistant project focuses on building an interactive chatbot without traditional coding, utilizing platforms such as Botpress, Chatbase, and Mizou AI. This approach enables rapid prototyping and deployment while maintaining customization.</p>

    <h3>Tools & Technologies Used</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Botpress</li>
      <li>Chatbase</li>
      <li>Mizou AI</li>
      <li>Google Dialogflow</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Process and Steps</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Requirement gathering and defining chatbot objectives.</li>
      <li>Platform selection and initial setup.</li>
      <li>Dialog flow design and training the chatbot.</li>
      <li>Testing and refinement based on user interactions.</li>
      <li>Deployment and monitoring chatbot performance.</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Outcomes and Learnings</h3>
    <p>This project enhanced my ability to design user-friendly AI assistants and understand the trade-offs between no-code and custom-coded solutions.</p>

    <h3>Code Sample</h3>
    <pre>
{
  "intents": [
    {
      "name": "greeting",
      "examples": ["Hello", "Hi", "Good morning"],
      "responses": ["Hello! How can I assist you today?"]
    }
  ]
}
    </pre>

    <h3>Reflection</h3>
    <p>Developing this chatbot highlighted the importance of conversational design, user experience, and iterative learning to improve AI assistants’ effectiveness.</p>
  </section>

